<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" >
<meta name="apple-touch-fullscreen" content="yes">
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no">
<meta name="ML-Config" content="fullscreen=yes,preventMove=no">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<!-- 全局控制 -->
<script src="scripts/viewport.js?v=26"></script>
<script src="scripts/jquery.js?v=27"></script>
<script src="scripts/ui_control.js?v=27"></script>
<link href="styles/global.css?v=27" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="styles/ui.css?v=27" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="styles/ui_ico.css?v=27" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="styles/ui_style.css?v=27" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="styles/ui_pull.css?v=27" rel="stylesheet">
<!-- end -->
<script src="scripts/submit_order.js?v=26"></script>
<link href="styles/submit_order.css" rel="stylesheet">
<title>提交订单</title>
<style>
.checkin .date:after{content:"入住"}
.checkout .date:after{content:"离店"}
.checkin_time:before{ content:"共"}
.checkin_time:after{ content:"晚"}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="order_intro">
	<div class="hotelname">广州天美酒店公寓</div>
    <div class="datetime">09月15日-09月16日  共1晚</div>
    <div class="room_type">房型:高级双人房</div>
	<div class="sever">双床  25㎡  宽带 双早</div>
</header>
<!-- 预订 -->
<div class="form_list">
	<div class="item ui_btn_block room_num">
    	<span>房间数</span>
        <span class="num">前台分配(2间)</span>
    </div>
	<div class="item">
    	<span>入住人</span>
        <input type="text" required class="person" placeholder="请输入姓名">
    </div>
	<div class="item">
    	<span>手机号</span>
        <input type="tel" required class="phone" placeholder="请输入手机号">
    </div>
</div>
<!-- 以上为预订部分 -->
<!-- 续住 -->
<script src="scripts/calendar.js"></script>
<script src="scripts/date.js"></script>
<link href="styles/calendar.css" rel="stylesheet">
<input type="hidden" id="startdate" name="startdate" value="" />
<input type="hidden" id="enddate" name="enddate" value="" />
<div class="form_list">
	<div class="item ui_btn_block ">
    	<span>续住时间</span>
        <div class="checkdate" id='checkdate'>
            <span class="checkin" id='checkin'><span class="date">1月1日</span></span>
            <span class="checkout" id='checkout'><span class="date">1月1日</span></span>
            <span class="checkin_time ui_color">1</span>
        </div>
    </div>
	<div class="item">
    	<span>续住房型</span>
        <span>高级双人房</span>
    </div>
	<div class="item ui_btn_block">
    	<span>续住房号</span>
        <span>8899</span>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- 以上为 续住 部分 -->
<div class="form_list">
	<div class="item">
    	<span>连住优惠</span>
        <span class="pay_way ischeck"><em class="ui_ico ui_ico13"></em><span>连住3天抵减300元</span></span>
    </div>
	<div class="item">
    	<span>积分抵用</span>
        <input type="tel" placeholder="积分抵房价(可用1860分/186元)">
    </div>
	<div class="item ui_btn_block usevote">
    	<span>优惠券</span>
        <span>不适用/不使用</span>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="form_list">
	<div class="item pay_list">
    	<span>支付方式</span>
        <ul>
            <li class="pay_way ischeck"><em class="ui_ico ui_ico13"></em><span>微信支付</span></li>
            <li class="pay_way"><em class="ui_ico ui_ico13"></em><span>到店支付</span></li>
			<!-- 续住时不显示以下 会员卡支付 方式 -->
            <li class="pay_way"><em class="ui_ico ui_ico13"></em><span>会员卡余额支付(<tt class="ui_price">568.89</tt>)</span></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="notic">
	<div class="title">温馨提示</div>
    <div class="content">
    	<p>1.支付说明：微信支付或积分支付不可取消，房间将整晚为您保留；到店支付房间保留至入住当天18:00，钟点房仅限8～10点入住。</p>
        <p>2.返券说明：本单使用优惠券后不可获取返券，未使用优惠券情况下可获得200元住房优惠券。</p>
    </div>
</div>
<div style="padding-top:15%">
    <div class="footfixed">
    	<div class="total ui_color">合计 <span class="ui_price">389</span> <del class="ui_price">389</del></div>
        <a href="submit_results.html" class="submit_btn">提交订单</a>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="ui_pull chooseroom_pull" style="display:none">
    <div class="list">
        <div class="default ischoose">前台分配(<span>2</span>间)</div>
        <div class="item">
            <div class="room_name">商务大床房(<span>3</span>间)</div>
            <div class="roomid"><span>204</span>(无烟层  有窗  近电梯)</div>
            <div class="roomid"><span>205</span>(无烟层  有窗  近电梯)</div>
            <div class="roomid"><span>206</span>(无烟层  有窗  近电梯)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <div class="room_name">商务大床房(<span>4</span>间)</div>
            <div class="roomid"><span>207</span>(无烟层  有窗  近电梯)</div>
            <div class="roomid"><span>208</span>(无烟层  有窗  近电梯)</div>
            <div class="roomid"><span>209</span>(无烟层  有窗  近电梯)</div>
            <div class="roomid"><span>210</span>(无烟层  有窗  近电梯)</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div style="padding-top:18%"><div class="sure_btn">确定</div></div>
</div>


<div class="ui_pull vote_pull">
    <div class="notic">
        <div class="title">温馨提示</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>1.原则上每个间夜仅可使用 1 张住房抵用券，特殊注明可叠加使用多张券的房型除外</p>
            <p>2.抵用券不找零、不兑换，使用后不可取消，请谨慎使用</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <ul class="votelist">
    	<li class="ischeck">
        	<em class="ui_ico ui_ico13"></em>
            <div class="ui_vote">
            	<p class="bordertop_img"></p>
                <div class="vote_con">
            	<p class="price">50元</p>
            	<p class="votename">高级大床房抵价券</p>
                <p class="limit">仅限碧桂园凤凰酒店集团使用</p>
                <p class="val_date">有效期至2015.12.31</p>
                </div>         
            	<p class="borderbtom_img"></p>  
            </div>
        </li>
    	<li>
        	<em class="ui_ico ui_ico13"></em>
            <div class="ui_vote">
            	<p class="bordertop_img"></p>
                <div class="vote_con">
            	<p class="price">50元</p>
            	<p class="votename">高级大床房抵价券</p>
                <p class="limit">仅限碧桂园凤凰酒店集团使用</p>
                <p class="val_date">有效期至2015.12.31</p>
                </div>         
            	<p class="borderbtom_img"></p>  
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <div style="padding-top:18%"><div class="footbtn">确定</div></div>
</div>
</body>
<script>
$(function(){
	$('.votelist li').click(function(){
		$(this).addClass('ischeck').siblings().removeClass('ischeck');
	})
	$('.usevote').click(function(){
		toshow($('.vote_pull'));
	})
	$('.vote_pull .footbtn').click(function(){
		toclose();
	})
})
</script>
</html>
